  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/transportation/\" rel=\"tag\">交通相关</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/25/ducati-wifi-airbag-jacket/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/9732c938225d6053a7c322700c570875/ducati_jacket.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 395px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n尽管正常来说「铁包皮（汽车）」都要比「皮包铁（摩托车）」安全一些，但向往急速飞驰时风声过耳那种快感的骑士还是大有人在。为了让这些人可以更安心地上路（怎么听上去怪怪的...），Ducati 和 Dainese 联手开发了一套全新的安全系统。它的名字叫 Ducati Multistrada D-Air，由设在电子系统内的感应器（用于监测车辆的加速度、刹车和导向状态）和机车夹克内的安全气囊组成。<br />\n<br />\n当前者搜集到潜在的事故数据时，会通过 Wi-Fi 向夹克发送信号，这样在车祸真正发生前，衣服内的安全气囊就会提前打开，从而达到保护驾驶者的目的。据悉首批搭载该系统的摩托车和夹克将会于五月在欧洲开卖，不知道会有多少人感兴趣呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/03/25/ducati-wifi-airbag-jacket/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.gizmag.com/ducati-motorcycle-airbag-jackets-d-air/31351/\" target=\"_blank\">Gizmag</a></span>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.wired.com/autopia/2014/03/ducati-multistrada-d-air/\" target=\"_blank\">Wired</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.ducatiuk.com/news/ducati_announces_world_s_first_production_motorcycle_wirelessly_integrated_with_airbag_riding_jackets___the_multistrada_d_air_/2014/03/21/3147/index.do\" target=\"_blank\">Ducati</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/25/ducati-wifi-airbag-jacket/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20856034/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/25/ducati-wifi-airbag-jacket/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
